Wildrider and Speedbreaker land a little way from the base guns up. "This
is Decepticons Speedbeaker and Wildrider, turn off the lasers so we can get
in" Speedbreaker radiod to the base. "Yeah, is there any enemy bots in
there" Wildrider asks, leaking lubricant from the half of his face.
